```plantuml
@startuml victor369basu_Real-time-stock-market-prediction

actor Client
participant "producer.js" as Producer
participant "consumer.js" as Consumer
participant "ml_consumer.js" as MLConsumer
participant "tf_train.js" as Train
participant "tf_validate.js" as Validate
participant "tf_model.js" as Model
participant "pre_process.js" as PreProcess
participant "server.js" as Server
participant "InstantiateDB.js" as DB
participant "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "MongoDB" as MongoDB

Client -> Server: Request model training
Server -> Train: Initiate training
Train -> Model: Train LSTM model
Model -> Train: Return trained model
Train -> MongoDB: Save model weights
MongoDB -> Train: Acknowledge

Client -> Server: Request model validation
Server -> Validate: Initiate validation
Validate -> MongoDB: Retrieve test dataset
MongoDB -> Validate: Return test dataset
Validate -> Model: Validate model
Model -> Validate: Return validation results
Validate -> MongoDB: Save performance metrics
MongoDB -> Validate: Acknowledge

Client -> Producer: Start data ingestion
Producer -> Kafka: Publish stock data

Kafka -> Consumer: Stream stock data
Consumer -> MongoDB: Store stock data
MongoDB -> Consumer: Acknowledge

MLConsumer -> Kafka: Subscribe to stock data
Kafka -> MLConsumer: Stream live stock data
MLConsumer -> PreProcess: Preprocess data
PreProcess -> MLConsumer: Return scaled data
MLConsumer -> Model: Generate predictions
Model -> MLConsumer: Return predictions
MLConsumer -> MongoDB: Log predictions
MongoDB -> MLConsumer: Acknowledge

@enduml
```